Package bg.tu_varna.sit.a4.fn22621660.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CloseCommand
    Command implementation for closing the current JSON file.
    CreateCommand
    Command implementation for creating a JSON node at a specified path.
    DeleteCommand
    Command implementation for deleting a JSON node at a specified path.
    EditCommand
    Command implementation for editing (updating) a JSON node at a specified path.
    HelpCommand
    Command implementation for displaying help information about available commands.
    MoveCommand
    Command implementation for moving files from a source directory to a destination directory.
    OpenCommand
    Command implementation for opening and parsing a JSON file.
    PrintCommand
    Command implementation for printing the JSON content.
    SaveAsCommand
    Command implementation for saving the JSON content to a specified file path.
    SaveCommand
    Command implementation for saving the JSON content to the currently opened file path.
    SearchCommand
    Command implementation for searching a key in the JSON content.
    SetCommand
    This class represents a command to set a value in a JSON file managed by JsonFileManager.
